      <title>货币市场动荡之际英国银行抵制上调抵押贷款利率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-banks-resist-mortgage-rate-hikes-amid-money-market-turmoil-2025-01-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[业内消息人士称，随着英镑货币市场的压力持续到第二周，英国银行正在接受英国抵押贷款利润率下降和风险增加的现实，因为放贷意愿大于对融资成本上升的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-banks-resist-mortgage-rate-hikes-amid-money-market-turmoil-2025-01-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:18:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于负担能力和经济担忧迫在眉睫，维斯特里认为前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/british-homebuilder-vistry-warns-uncertain-market-conditions-2025-01-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国产量最大的房屋建筑商 Vistry 周三表示，由于住房行业面临负担能力和更广泛的经济困境，今年的市场状况仍然不确定，同时维持其 2024 年盈利预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/british-homebuilder-vistry-warns-uncertain-market-conditions-2025-01-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称，鉴于不确定性很高，欧洲央行必须谨慎降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-households-could-increase-consumption-ecb-chief-economist-says-2025-01-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行两名高级官员周三表示，欧洲央行今年可能会继续放松政策，但需要谨慎，因为从潜在的全球贸易战到国内政治等特殊不确定性给前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-households-could-increase-consumption-ecb-chief-economist-says-2025-01-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 03:44:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
