      <title>万事达卡同意就薪酬歧视诉讼支付 2600 万美元和解金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/mastercard-agrees-26-mln-settlement-pay-bias-lawsuit-2025-01-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周二的一份法庭文件显示，万事达卡已同意支付 2600 万美元并审计其雇佣行为，以解决其系统性地克扣全国约 7,500 名女性、黑人和西班牙裔员工工资的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/mastercard-agrees-26-mln-settlement-pay-bias-lawsuit-2025-01-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 18:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
