      <title>国际金融公司：世界必须紧急简化绿色债券“分类法”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/world-must-urgently-streamline-green-bond-taxonomies-ifc-2025-01-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行集团的私人投资部门表示，市场正准备迎接即将上任的特朗普政府对可持续投资的强烈反对，必须紧急简化绿色债券的定义，以吸引绿色转型所需的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/world-must-urgently-streamline-green-bond-taxonomies-ifc-2025-01-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
